{"tid":1542620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係啊我係分化撚。9.4販民完美示範維穩手段。","createTime":"2019-09-05T02:06:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T06:40:07.000Z","uid":195409,"like":38,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"130ef3e979f03a11cf4d48d3fc4ad21e61626c02","tid":1542620,"uid":195409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:06:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只有販民可以瓦解運動。<br />\n林鄭做咩都好，無販民配合維穩一定唔會成事。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n9.4有版大家睇，林鄭一個撤回，販民衝出黎維穩。<br />\n<br />\n94 #朱凱廸 改嗌「四大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n94 #岑子杰 提出弱雞版新五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n94 #梁家傑 稱應放眼區選，武力升級即中計<br />\n<br />\n94 #劉慧卿 指民主派希望邱騰華成為特首<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各有各做？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">建制同販民就真係各有各做</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">認清敵人係邊個先啦</span></span>連登仔！<br />\n<br />\n你地繼續屌我係分化撚，大家<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">未醒送個普選俾你地都無用</span></span>。"},{"pid":"d21d2910c82c54956df2e2f51ea5bc6231e70f78","tid":1542620,"uid":195409,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:09:17.000Z","msg":"自推一億次"},{"pid":"77953fa8d38b43d7ad5af8f350f8fed81747e17a","tid":1542620,"uid":195409,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:09:31.000Z","msg":"1/100000000"},{"pid":"35611c5bf8ce7b4373d3d9da452e949c3ea8ccfe","tid":1542620,"uid":195409,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:09:42.000Z","msg":"2/100000000"},{"pid":"255135bcd06e7eaec315bcf9882a04b55184a695","tid":1542620,"uid":49336,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:09:45.000Z","msg":"不推文"},{"pid":"2e4f6614cfc0df740ad2b05b514edbcb49658e76","tid":1542620,"uid":195409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:09:55.000Z","msg":"3/100000000"},{"pid":"7341c128e90e608d8d86bb5e99ecaa592035396d","tid":1542620,"uid":140326,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"repl